{"tid":2487774,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"三十秒科學–癌症所導致的體重流失(3)","createTime":"2021-04-13T22:11:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T03:45:36.000Z","uid":38861,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"966498014dd83e3736a5262e57da15af68fe30a3","tid":2487774,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T22:11:34.000Z","msg":"癌細胞從原位轉移到另一器官，亦即是Metastasis，是癌病患者主要的死因。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbtpHYrbTsX2v5ss93uhokayRDKDxgKZtHQ5wmgJ8UAYn?filename=k1L1yED.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk1L1yED.jpg&h=a3b77e16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「有趣的是」，癌細胞雖近乎不會轉移到肌肉位置裡頭，但卻能從遠處釋放物質，經由血管抵達肌肉位置，催使肌肉萎縮，亦即是癌症惡病質(cancer cachexia)。<br />\n<br />\n(圖2)肌肉萎縮不但之令病人變得虛弱，難以接近正常劑量的化療，更為致命的是，當心臟肌肉及橫隔膜肌肉亦遭受到萎縮的時候，病人便會因呼吸困難等問題而逝死。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmdd6cRyQNFAbvHvLiDGWoJCUUd7NKZFVgqDgsYkAJ2oFj?filename=2uxZ4Mk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2uxZ4Mk.jpg&h=c3cef303&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早在1858年已有科學家指出cancer cachexia的存在，但至今2021年仍是沒有FDA認可藥物治療cancer cachexia。<br />\n<br />\n(圖3)現時有不少臨床研究希望可以制衡cancer cachexia，普遍均是從營養方面入手。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYxe5YitenWHLYGACLbKXVBDkLPire2bEMSnWPdgUWW8e?filename=Au4Nuc2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAu4Nuc2.png&h=7239fdf9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但結果大多數是只能夠增加病人的脂肪組織，而沒能夠填補已萎縮的肌肉。<br />\n<br />\n有一點值得注意的是，肌肉細胞並非是死去，純粹是其分解蛋白質的進程比生產蛋白質的進程來得更快，因而形成萎縮。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(圖4)從研究Cancer cachexia的老鼠模型中可以看到，患癌的老鼠不但更為細小，其手腕的握力度亦有所下降。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNfMEnPEjqiD1jpoxkYFWyZQkUuDKAU1zELL45jDmaAGY?filename=gHe2h6s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgHe2h6s.png&h=5b8e5983&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n觀察肌肉細胞橫切面的面積時，亦可以看到肌肉細胞的面積明顯有所縮細。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下集將會講解Cancer cachexia的老鼠模型所得出的其中一道結果。<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單俾一個like以及Bookmark，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11KDCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=ee34766a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「買一嚿/半嚿薯仔」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11KDCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=aa303713\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除非Facebook及IG重開侵侵的account，否則我的IG將不會再作更新，只會寄居本土LIHKG及Penana。<br />\n <br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC6015555/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC6015555%2F&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11KDCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=0d6876c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC6015555/</a>"},{"pid":"9e0c11b488074bc6300730181e7fac262fec8167","tid":2487774,"uid":75487,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T22:12:32.000Z","msg":"買一舊！"},{"pid":"290a71188f821c511df065bb137bf5f8d2012b9f","tid":2487774,"uid":75487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e0c11b488074bc6300730181e7fac262fec8167","tid":2487774,"uid":75487,"l